WEBVTT

00:00.380 --> 00:02.202
Excuse me, can I take a picture here?

00:03.188 --> 00:04.266
Here in the lobby?

00:04.628 --> 00:05.410
Yes, you can.

00:05.741 --> 00:06.157
Good.

00:06.794 --> 00:08.329
And would you take a picture of us?

00:08.636 --> 00:08.951
Sure.

00:09.473 --> 00:10.007
Thank you.

00:10.499 --> 00:12.815
We want to have a picture taken with this Christmas Tree.

00:13.655 --> 00:16.689
You want a picture including the whole Christmas Tree, right?

00:17.074 --> 00:19.391
In that case, it will be vertically long.

00:19.902 --> 00:20.695
That's fine.

00:21.198 --> 00:22.706
Can you get all of us in the picture?

00:23.075 --> 00:25.171
Can you get closer to the center, everyone?

00:25.378 --> 00:26.270
Say cheese.

00:26.429 --> 00:27.141
Cheese!

00:27.801 --> 00:28.988
Can you take one more, please?

00:29.125 --> 00:29.959
No problem.

00:30.245 --> 00:31.187
Thank you very much.

